# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-03-05 21:40

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:7
translate spanish d18a_98123b48:

    # S "Hmm... and that curtain is blocking our access..."
    S "Hmm... y esa cortina nos bloquea el paso..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:10
translate spanish d18a_28e8f1bc:

    # Z "If there was a way our people could reach the Ta-Mehu, they would have..."
    Z "Si hubiera una forma de que nuestra gente pudiera llegar al Ta-Mehu, ya lo habrían hecho..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:11
translate spanish d18a_06b4cef9:

    # Z "Many have tried, but the mist curtain and northern winds from beyond Cairo make it impossible."
    Z "Muchos lo intentaron, pero la cortina de niebla y los vientos del norte más allá de El Cairo lo hacen imposible."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:12
translate spanish d18a_58504eb8:

    # Z "The places you have read about, like Alexandria, are beyond our reach... some say reclaimed by the sea, but nobody knows for certain."
    Z "Los lugares de los que has leído, como Alejandría, están fuera de nuestro alcance... algunos dicen que el mar los reclamó, pero nadie lo sabe seguro."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:15
translate spanish d18a_c51cf553:

    # S "I assume we are not the first ones to wonder what lies behind that curtain."
    S "Supongo que no seremos los primeros en preguntarnos qué hay detrás de esa cortina."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:18
translate spanish d18a_38dac809:

    # Z "Of course, as is only natural, but there is only one kind of people who could survive such a trip... Even I never ventured further than some parts of Old Cairo."
    Z "Por supuesto, es lo natural... pero sólo hay un tipo de personas que podría sobrevivir a ese viaje... Ni yo me he aventurado más allá de algunas partes del Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:19
translate spanish d18a_6e0f25ef:

    # Z "It is said that there is nothing of sustenance to feed from, and there are not enough filters to keep your lungs from eventually burning up."
    Z "Se dice que allí no hay nada de lo que alimentarse, y que no hay suficientes filtros para evitar que te ardan los pulmones."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:22
translate spanish d18a_56a4dd25:

    # S "Funny to think about it... the Temple does have lessons about what the Ta-Mehu might have looked like, in ancient times..."
    S "Da risa pensarlo... el Templo da clases sobre cómo era el Ta-Mehu en tiempos antiguos..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:23
translate spanish d18a_44955e4c:

    # S "They make it sound like we are but a few hours driving away from the promised land, and then tell us that we can never reach it."
    S "Lo pintan como si estuviera a unas pocas horas en coche del paraíso prometido... y luego te dicen que jamás podrás alcanzarlo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:26
translate spanish d18a_23efbae2:

    # Z "You would not be the first Stalker who instead of being cowed into obedience by the Temple's teachings is stirred into curiosity..."
    Z "No serías la primera Acechadora que, en vez de dejarse amedrentar por las enseñanzas del Templo, siente curiosidad..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:27
translate spanish d18a_a7b7f837:

    # Z "Maybe one day you will want to find out. I warn you though. Those who have tried to cross beyond, either did not return or came back with horror stories."
    Z "Quizá algún día quieras descubrirlo. Pero te advierto: los que lo intentaron o no volvieron, o regresaron contando historias de horror."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:28
translate spanish d18a_419b5d59:

    # Z "We lost some seasoned Stalkers, that way."
    Z "Así perdimos a algunos Acechadores curtidos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:33
translate spanish d18a_090c2755:

    # E "Master... Lady [S]..."
    E "Amo... Señorita [S]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:36
translate spanish d18a_54a1ae42:

    # E "I have brought some refreshments."
    E "He traído algunos refrescos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:39
translate spanish d18a_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:40
translate spanish d18a_d34087e8:

    # Z "We appreciate it. Is dinner being prepared? I might have things to do later."
    Z "Te lo agradecemos. ¿Se está preparando la cena? Quizá luego tenga cosas que hacer."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:42
translate spanish d18a_800e4352:

    # E "Lady Kateryna is in the kitchen, master. She is really taking charge there."
    E "La señora Kateryna está en la cocina, amo. Se está haciendo cargo de la situación."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:43
translate spanish d18a_6170195e:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} I believe you."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Me lo creo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:45
translate spanish d18a_347e02ff:

    # E "Yes, master, I will have everything ready in about thirty minutes."
    E "Sí, amo, tendré todo listo en unos treinta minutos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:46
translate spanish d18a_e8dc0b42:

    # Z "Good."
    Z "Bien."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:49
translate spanish d18a_4815d357:

    # E "Is there anything else I can do for you, Master?"
    E "¿Hay algo más que pueda hacer por ti, amo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:55
translate spanish d18a_dffa3320:

    # Z "Yes, there is. But first, the refreshments"
    Z "Sí, lo hay. Pero primero, los refrescos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:58
translate spanish d18a_4ad4d65b:

    # "She serves you..."
    "Ella te sirve..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:61
translate spanish d18a_157fcc04:

    # E "Master?"
    E "¿Amo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:64
translate spanish d18a_ccf17902:

    # Z "My [persistent.da] and I are talking about the mysteries surrounding the Ta-Mehu."
    Z "Mi [persistent.da] y yo estamos hablando sobre los misterios que rodean al Ta-Mehu."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:65
translate spanish d18a_946ac6a1:

    # Z "Sit with us. I would like to hear your perspective."
    Z "Siéntate con nosotros. Me gustaría escuchar tu perspectiva."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:68
translate spanish d18a_9381cd7e:

    # E "Oh... Master... I don't follow...?"
    E "Oh... Amo... No te entiendo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:69
translate spanish d18a_281c7577:

    # Z "You heard me. The kitchen can miss you for a few minutes."
    Z "Me has oído. La cocina puede prescindir de ti unos minutos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:72
translate spanish d18a_b017e082:

    # Z "Sit here."
    Z "Siéntate aquí."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:75
translate spanish d18a_edf01c8b:

    # "She hesitantly sits down..."
    "Se sienta con cierta vacilación..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:78
translate spanish d18a_7919fcd3:

    # E "Master... this is not appropriate."
    E "Amo... esto no es apropiado."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:84
translate spanish d18a_503cd53b:

    # Z "I have questions for Emilia the person, not for the slave."
    Z "Tengo preguntas para Emilia, la persona, no para la esclava."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:87
translate spanish d18a_818a8031:

    # Z "It is, if I deem it to be, Emilia."
    Z "Lo es, si yo lo decido, Emilia."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:90
translate spanish d18a_5286cc18:

    # Z "Now... remind me. I believe the Queen mentioned you coming from the far West..."
    Z "Ahora... recuérdame. Creo que la Reina mencionó que venías del lejano oeste..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:93
translate spanish d18a_30130734:

    # E "Yes, Master. A remote oasis a few days of travel on foot."
    E "Sí, Amo. Un oasis remoto, a unos días de viaje a pie."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:95
translate spanish d18a_4d78ea65:

    # Z "Were you travelling, before the royal guards took you here?"
    Z "¿Viajabas antes de que los guardias reales te trajeran aquí?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:98
translate spanish d18a_0b6c297e:

    # E "I have lived and served most of my adult life in that oasis, Master."
    E "Viví y serví casi toda mi vida adulta en ese oasis, Amo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:102
translate spanish d18a_9ed8c9e5:

    # S "How remote can it be, if the distance is measured in days of travel?"
    S "¿Tan remoto puede ser, si se mide en días de viaje?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:105
translate spanish d18a_e609d471:

    # E "Maybe isolated is a better word. We had very limited interaction with outsiders."
    E "Quizá 'aislado' sea una palabra más adecuada. Teníamos muy poca interacción con forasteros."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:108
translate spanish d18a_8f3882ae:

    # S "Were there no visitors, traveling merchants troupes, crossing?"
    S "¿No había visitantes, comerciantes viajeros, caravanas?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:111
translate spanish d18a_a8f31c3b:

    # "Very rarely, but I was never allowed in their presence, so I would not know who they were."
    "Muy rara vez, pero nunca me permitían estar en su presencia, así que no sabría decir quiénes eran."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:114
translate spanish d18a_7cfb63d9:

    # S "And before that time in your life? Have you heard anything about the big sea in the North?"
    S "¿Y antes de esa etapa de tu vida? ¿Has oído hablar del gran mar del norte?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:117
translate spanish d18a_fc198621:

    # E "I...know of the sea from the stories my mother told me, but have never seen it. As I changed masters, I only saw desert, much like here."
    E "Conozco el mar por las historias que me contaba mi madre, pero nunca lo he visto. Conforme fui cambiando de amo, sólo vi desierto, igual que aquí."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:120
translate spanish d18a_8462e390:

    # Z "And what about the time you were serving the Queen? Have you heard any stories?"
    Z "¿Y durante el tiempo que serviste a la Reina? ¿Escuchaste alguna historia?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:123
translate spanish d18a_32ffe307:

    # E "Oh, yes... I served the Queen personally many times, even during her throne hearings. I have worn the mask, sometimes."
    E "Oh, sí... Serví personalmente a la Reina muchas veces, incluso durante sus audiencias en el trono. A veces llevaba la máscara."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:126
translate spanish d18a_63d65514:

    # E "I heard many stories, I learned so much from listening, just by attending the hearings."
    E "Escuché muchas historias, aprendí mucho simplemente asistiendo a las audiencias."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:129
translate spanish d18a_ed2c6289:

    # E "I am sure that the Queen would like me to forget some of those tales... {i}*chuckles*{/i}"
    E "Estoy segura de que a la Reina le gustaría que olvidara algunas de esas historias... {i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:134
translate spanish d18a_8692db66:

    # S "Is there any place that fascinates you the most? A place you would like to visit?"
    S "¿Hay algún lugar que te fascine especialmente? ¿Un sitio al que te gustaría viajar?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:137
translate spanish d18a_b3eea215:

    # E "I... don't know... In my place, I find it best not to daydream too much..."
    E "No lo sé... En mi posición, creo que es mejor no soñar demasiado despierta..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:140
translate spanish d18a_5098b15c:

    # "She hesitates for a second, before continuing."
    "Ella duda durante un segundo, antes de continuar."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:143
translate spanish d18a_9e8191ae:

    # E "I think... I would like to see the place where I was born, as I have no real memory of it, if not through the retelling of others."
    E "Creo... que me gustaría ver el lugar donde nací, ya que no tengo recuerdos reales, salvo por lo que me contaron otros."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:146
translate spanish d18a_9cc5594f:

    # Z "Where is this place?"
    Z "¿Dónde está ese lugar?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:149
translate spanish d18a_e1f41130:

    # E "Before we were separated, when I was still a child, I asked my mother this. But I could tell that the question would make her sad, so eventually I stopped asking."
    E "Antes de que nos separaran, cuando aún era una niña, le pregunté a mi madre. Pero podía notar que esa pregunta la entristecía, así que al final dejé de insistir."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:150
translate spanish d18a_d3955a2d:

    # E "Later I tried asking my master, but he would brush off the question, or beat me for forgetting my place."
    E "Después intenté preguntarle a mi amo, pero o bien me evitaba la respuesta, o me golpeaba por olvidarme de mi lugar."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:153
translate spanish d18a_0763b2b2:

    # E "I... never got a clear answer from him... except this one time, when he was laying with me."
    E "Yo... Nunca obtuve una respuesta clara de él... salvo aquella vez, cuando yacía conmigo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:156
translate spanish d18a_ef31dc99:

    # E "I remember him talking about a small village, where several of the slaves shared the same physical traits, like my mother and myself."
    E "Recuerdo que hablaba de un pequeño pueblo, donde varios esclavos compartían los mismos rasgos físicos, como mi madre y yo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:159
translate spanish d18a_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:162
translate spanish d18a_f5624b82:

    # S "That's... fascinating. And the way you describe it, mysterious, too."
    S "Eso... es fascinante. Y por cómo lo describes, también parece misterioso."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:163
translate spanish d18a_7c024f6d:

    # S "Maybe I will look for this place, one day, who knows?"
    S "Quizá un día busque ese lugar, ¿quién sabe?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:166
translate spanish d18a_7f366e85:

    # E "I... appreciate your words, Lady [S], but I am happy here, with Master [persistent.player_name]."
    E "Yo... agradezco tus palabras, señora [S], pero soy feliz aquí, con el amo [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:169
translate spanish d18a_7030966b:

    # E "Even if I was to learn where this place is, I would not truly ask to see it."
    E "Aunque llegara a saber dónde está ese lugar, no pediría verlo de verdad."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:172
translate spanish d18a_3e7d51bf:

    # E "I know my place, mistress, and I could not wish for better masters than I have now."
    E "Sé cuál es mi sitio, señora, y no podría desear mejores amos que los que tengo ahora."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:175
translate spanish d18a_8585d873:

    # "You notice in her body language a sense of unfamiliarity, and perhaps even discomfort, as she looks around and finds herself seated like a guest rather than at the feet of her masters."
    "Notas en su lenguaje corporal cierta incomodidad, quizá incluso nerviosismo, al verse sentada como una invitada en lugar de estar a los pies de sus amos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:178
translate spanish d18a_b58c6e01:

    # "To ease her discomfort, you eventually change the subject and allow her to resume her duties."
    "Para aliviar su incomodidad, cambias de tema y permites que retome sus deberes."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:185
translate spanish d18a_d0427f1c:

    # Z "There is something you could do. Give my [persistent.da] a good shoulder rub, will you?"
    Z "Hay algo que podrías hacer. Dale un buen masaje en los hombros a mi [persistent.da], ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:188
translate spanish d18a_ff8a7640:

    # E "With pleasure, Master."
    E "Con mucho gusto, amo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:191
translate spanish d18a_55308084:

    # "She takes place behind [S]..."
    "Ella se coloca detrás de [S]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:194
translate spanish d18a_5006731d:

    # S "Well, thank you, [persistent.dad]..."
    S "Bueno, gracias, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:195
translate spanish d18a_ccb5f6a8:

    # E "Please let me know if I apply too much pressure."
    E "Por favor, avísame si ejerzo demasiada presión."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:196
translate spanish d18a_0343aa89:

    # S "Sure..."
    S "Claro..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:199
translate spanish d18a_9275617e:

    # "Your maid starts kneading [S]'s shoulders with practiced skill."
    "Tu sirvienta empieza a masajear los hombros de [S] con destreza."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:200
translate spanish d18a_2425f46e:

    # S "That's... not bad."
    S "Eso... no está mal."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:203
translate spanish d18a_a42369a1:

    # S "Why didn't we have this when I was younger, hm?"
    S "¿Por qué no teníamos esto cuando era más joven, hm?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:204
translate spanish d18a_365b00e6:

    # S "Didn't you think your little princess deserved it?"
    S "¿No pensabas que tu pequeña princesa lo merecía?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:207
translate spanish d18a_5d45341c:

    # Z "I don't know that you would have appreciated her services the way you do now ."
    Z "No sé si entonces habrías apreciado sus servicios como lo haces ahora."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:210
translate spanish d18a_e624f0da:

    # S "You... might have a point..."
    S "Puede que... tengas razón..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:211
translate spanish d18a_a4e6b03a:

    # "Emilia glides her hands over her skin, as if playing a familiar instrument..."
    "Emilia desliza sus manos sobre su piel, como si tocara un instrumento que conoce bien..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:212
translate spanish d18a_19ea47c5:

    # S "She's... very good."
    S "Ella... es muy buena."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:215
translate spanish d18a_fe183326:

    # Z "She can be even better, if you want."
    Z "Puede ser aún mejor, si quieres."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:218
translate spanish d18a_f7b83074:

    # S "I was going to ask how you know, but that's a dumb question..."
    S "Iba a preguntarte cómo lo sabes, pero sería una pregunta estúpida..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:221
translate spanish d18a_62839e5b:

    # Z "I'm just saying that Emilia has many talents."
    Z "Solo digo que Emilia tiene muchos talentos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:224
translate spanish d18a_c2c63887:

    # "As Emilia gently massages your [persistent.da]'s neck, you are struck by the erotic vibe that hangs in the room."
    "Mientras Emilia masajea suavemente el cuello de tu [persistent.da], te impacta la carga erótica que empieza a flotar en el ambiente."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:225
translate spanish d18a_d859649a:

    # "Is it a product of your mind, based on your previous experiences with both Emilia and [S]? Did you catch a mutual glance between them?"
    "¿Será producto de tu imaginación, basada en tus experiencias anteriores con Emilia y [S]? ¿Captaste alguna mirada cómplice entre ellas?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:226
translate spanish d18a_ec18b94d:

    # "Or are you letting your testosterone do the thinking, engaging the notion of these two women playing with each other in an erotic spectacle for your benefit?"
    "¿O simplemente estás dejando que tu testosterona se adueñe de tus pensamientos, imaginando a esas dos mujeres jugueteando entre ellas para tu disfrute?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:229
translate spanish d18a_908e7a79:

    # S "It's... better for you to stop now... I almost forget what we talked about..."
    S "Será... mejor que pares ya... casi olvido de qué estábamos hablando..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:232
translate spanish d18a_07ffeba1:

    # E "As you wish, my lady..."
    E "Como desees, mi señora..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:235
translate spanish d18a_f87977f9:

    # S "My [persistent.dad] and I could use some snacks, would you bring us some?"
    S "A mi [persistent.dad] y a mí nos vendrían bien unos aperitivos, ¿nos traerías algunos?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:238
translate spanish d18a_94c02e50:

    # E "Of course. I will be right back."
    E "Por supuesto. Vuelvo enseguida."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:241
translate spanish d18a_7f4d2d74:

    # "Whatever it was, you have a feeling that [S] too was sensing something in the air, and decided to cut it short."
    "Sea lo que fuera, tienes la sensación de que [S] también notó algo en el ambiente, y decidió cortarlo de raíz."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:244
translate spanish d18a_17f454a4:

    # "She leaves the room..."
    "Ella sale de la habitación..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:247
translate spanish d18a_2f34f101:

    # S "That was... relaxing... so where did we stop?"
    S "Eso fue... relajante... ¿por dónde nos habíamos quedado?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:252
translate spanish d18a_f0f4dec4:

    # "You two continue chatting for a while, before each going about the rest of your days."
    "Seguís charlando un rato más, antes de que cada uno siga con el resto de su día."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:261
translate spanish d18b_0be08983:

    # "On the way into the inner city, near the gates, market stalls are being set up and citizens begin to gather."
    "De camino a la ciudad interior, cerca de las puertas, se están montando los puestos del mercado y los ciudadanos empiezan a reunirse."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:262
translate spanish d18b_1e81d439:

    # "The crowd here is not as dense as in the heart of the market, where the fresh produce draws the largest gatherings."
    "La multitud aquí no es tan densa como en el corazón del mercado, donde los productos frescos atraen a más gente."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:265
translate spanish d18b_aba6d1c4:

    # "The trade of slaves, which occurs on specific appointed days such as today, is a lively affair so there's a fair amount of people around here as well."
    "El comercio de esclavos, que tiene lugar en días específicos como hoy, es un asunto animado, así que también hay bastante movimiento por aquí."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:266
translate spanish d18b_0dd3aeda:

    # "You have no intention of buying a slave, and are here primarily to escort [A], who is tasked by [W] with buying some spices for the kitchen."
    "No tienes intención de comprar una esclava; estás aquí principalmente para acompañar a [A], a quien [W] encargó comprar algunas especias para la cocina."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:269
translate spanish d18b_075e09f3:

    # A "There is still enough to see around here! And we avoid the crowds."
    A "¡Todavía hay mucho que ver por aquí! Y además evitamos las multitudes."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:270
translate spanish d18b_142a2ab3:

    # Z "Good.. That way, there is less of a chance for a certain girl to get in trouble again."
    Z "Bien... Así hay menos posibilidades de que cierta niña vuelva a meterse en líos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:273
translate spanish d18b_0e83012c:

    # A "I don't think we need to worry about that [persistent.dad]. See that guard over there?"
    A "No creo que tengamos que preocuparnos por eso, [persistent.dad]. ¿Ves a ese guardia de allí?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:276
translate spanish d18b_11633f08:

    # Z "Yes, it seems the accident was taken seriously and they have increased their presence."
    Z "Sí, parece que se han tomado en serio el accidente y han aumentado su presencia."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:277
translate spanish d18b_dba24d7f:

    # Z "If you have found the spices, is there anything else you want to see?"
    Z "Si ya has encontrado las especias, ¿hay algo más que quieras ver?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:280
translate spanish d18b_5307a6cf:

    # A "If you let me, I would like to look for a new dressmaker. I have an idea for [S]."
    A "Si me dejas, me gustaría buscar una nueva modista. Tengo una idea para [S]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:283
translate spanish d18b_eae46a27:

    # Z "We can take a look. I think there are a few new vendors in the market."
    Z "Podemos echar un vistazo. Creo que hay algunos vendedores nuevos en el mercado."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:288
translate spanish d18b_6ddfdd63:

    # "As you walk around trying to keep an eye on [A], you observe the lively market and the Zetan citizens that populate it."
    "Mientras paseas intentando vigilar a [A], observas el mercado bullicioso y a los ciudadanos zetanos que lo llenan."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:291
translate spanish d18b_d547f409:

    # Ci "I told you already. That slave had the audacity to call me old!"
    Ci "Ya te lo dije. ¡Ese esclavo tuvo la osadía de llamarme vieja!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:294
translate spanish d18b_49ddf698:

    # G "My lady, I have spoken to his Master. This is a minor matter and the City will not have a say in it. If the Master deems it appropriate, he will punish the slave."
    G "Mi señora, he hablado con su amo. Es un asunto menor y la Ciudad no tendrá nada que decir al respecto. Si su amo lo considera apropiado, castigará al esclavo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:296
translate spanish d18b_d9a5d786:

    # "Your leisurely walk confirms your thoughts. There are plenty of new faces. One person, however, you know... a slaveholder of some repute who has risen to be a Queen's legate, named Khalil."
    "Tu paseo relajado confirma tus sospechas. Hay muchas caras nuevas. Sin embargo, reconoces a una persona... un tratante de esclavos de cierta reputación que ha ascendido hasta convertirse en legado de la Reina: Khalil."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:299
translate spanish d18b_6640f4d6:

    # Kha "Stalker [persistent.player_name]..."
    Kha "Acechador [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:300
translate spanish d18b_04661a63:

    # Z "Legate Khalil. Have you decided to set aside the game of politics? What brings you to mingle with the common folk?"
    Z "Legado Khalil. ¿Has decidido dejar de lado los juegos de la política? ¿Qué te trae a mezclarse con el pueblo llano?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:303
translate spanish d18b_58bdf772:

    # Kha "The wheels of that game are ever turning, Stalker [persistent.player_name]. I am happy to say that the Queen and the Elders seem to appreciate my efforts for the betterment of the city."
    Kha "Las ruedas de ese juego nunca dejan de girar, Acechador [persistent.player_name]. Me alegra decir que la Reina y los Ancianos parecen valorar mis esfuerzos por mejorar la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:304
translate spanish d18b_3d27ce86:

    # Kha "And who knows, a further raise in station might be within reach, with patience and perserverance."
    Kha "Y quién sabe, quizá con paciencia y perseverancia logre ascender aún más."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:305
translate spanish d18b_5f8ee22f:

    # Kha "And as for my presence here... I find it good practice to occasionally show the members of my house how we got where we got in the first place."
    Kha "En cuanto a mi presencia aquí... creo que es buena práctica mostrar de vez en cuando a los miembros de mi casa cómo llegamos hasta donde estamos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:306
translate spanish d18b_838594b5:

    # Kha "They need to be reminded who is in charge."
    Kha "Hay que recordarles quién manda."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:309
translate spanish d18b_ad048822:

    # Z "Leading by example is always the best approach."
    Z "Predicar con el ejemplo siempre es la mejor estrategia."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:310
translate spanish d18b_a53a0536:

    # "This man is an old associate, though not necessarily a friend like Igor."
    "Este hombre es un viejo conocido, aunque no necesariamente un amigo como Igor."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:311
translate spanish d18b_47d2d801:

    # "The nature of your relationship is more opportunistic, but still based on mutual consideration for your respective accomplishments."
    "La naturaleza de vuestra relación es más bien oportunista, aunque basada en el respeto mutuo por vuestros logros."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:312
translate spanish d18b_bb98675a:

    # "On more than one occasion, his insights in matters of war and diplomacy have proved to be precious."
    "En más de una ocasión, sus conocimientos en temas de guerra y diplomacia han sido muy valiosos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:313
translate spanish d18b_a9ec690f:

    # "Likewise, in preparation to leading men into battle, he has drawn on your knowledge of the lay of the lands and your scouting services."
    "Del mismo modo, cuando se preparaba para liderar hombres en batalla, recurrió a tu experiencia sobre el terreno y tus servicios de rastreo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:317
translate spanish d18b_ec2fb8d6:

    # Kha "I take this is your second [persistent.da]? This is the first time I see her. What's her name?"
    Kha "Supongo que esta es tu segunda [persistent.da], ¿no? Es la primera vez que la veo. ¿Cómo se llama?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:319
translate spanish d18b_71c48214:

    # Kha "Who is this beautiful lady accompanying you? This is the first time I see her. What's her name?"
    Kha "¿Quién es esta hermosa dama que te acompaña? Es la primera vez que la veo. ¿Cómo se llama?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:322
translate spanish d18b_7612173d:

    # "His eyes linger on [A]'s figure..."
    "Sus ojos se posan en la figura de [A]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:325
translate spanish d18b_efab3b79:

    # Z "Her name is [A]."
    Z "Se llama [A]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:328
translate spanish d18b_d7d1739e:

    # Kha "I compliment your wife, Stalker. A pretty face, ample chest and fair skin. She's attractive and, I would imagine, fertile."
    Kha "Felicito a tu esposa, Acechador. Un rostro bonito, un pecho generoso y una piel clara. Es atractiva y, me imagino, fértil."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:332
translate spanish d18b_5766a441:

    # Kha "[persistent.da!c]s are a beautiful thing, aren't they?"
    Kha "Las [persistent.da!c] son una maravilla, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:333
translate spanish d18b_53f6a125:

    # Kha "I hope she is doing you properly, or are you keeping her untouched to raise her value to those that favour such things?"
    Kha "Espero que te esté sirviendo como es debido... o acaso la estás reservando intacta para aumentar su valor ante quienes prefieren esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:334
translate spanish d18b_aaeba2b2:

    # "Legate Khalil was never a man for polite conversation. Direct in his ways and a stark traditionalist at heart, he sees only one purpose for most of the women he encounters..."
    "El Legado Khalil nunca fue un hombre de palabras educadas. Directo en sus maneras y tradicionalista hasta la médula, sólo ve un propósito para la mayoría de las mujeres con las que se cruza..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:338
translate spanish d18b_84bf37e5:

    # A "Am I, [persistent.dad]...?"
    A "¿Lo soy, [persistent.dad]...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:340
translate spanish d18b_f34006ce:

    # A "Am I...?"
    A "¿Lo soy...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:343
translate spanish d18b_6c58a532:

    # "She looks your way, suddenly shy..."
    "Ella te mira, de repente tímida..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:346
translate spanish d18b_876481a2:

    # Z "You are indeed."
    Z "Lo eres, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:349
translate spanish d18b_a20cfeac:

    # Z "That's not why I care for you, [A], you know that."
    Z "Pero no es por eso que me importas, [A], lo sabes."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:353
translate spanish d18b_279c9dce:

    # A "I know, [persistent.dad]..."
    A "Lo sé, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:355
translate spanish d18b_f8a2dda5:

    # A "I know. {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    A "Lo sé. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:361
translate spanish d18b_940c4599:

    # Kha "On a different topic, I understand congratulations are in order."
    Kha "Cambiando de tema, entiendo que debo felicitarte."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:362
translate spanish d18b_ecd8eeac:

    # Kha "The rumors go around that your firstborn has successfully survived her first contact trial in a Zone."
    Kha "Los rumores dicen que tu primogénita ha superado con éxito su primera prueba de contacto en una Zona."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:363
translate spanish d18b_e54f40fd:

    # Z "Yes. She did well."
    Z "Sí. Lo hizo bien."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:367
translate spanish d18b_28b7a492:

    # A "Is this your daughter?"
    A "¿Es tu hija?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:369
translate spanish d18b_9c09cc54:

    # A "Is this a slave?"
    A "¿O es una esclava?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:372
translate spanish d18b_3be78cd6:

    # "Intervening, [A] deflects the conversation away from her elder sister. "
    "Interviniendo, [A] desvía la conversación lejos de su hermana mayor."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:373
translate spanish d18b_efc0599f:

    # Kha "She is one of many, yes. But she is not for sale today."
    Kha "Es una entre muchas, sí. Pero hoy no está a la venta."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:376
translate spanish d18b_8ba95f3f:

    # Kha "However, if Stalker [persistent.player_name] is interested in some of my other wares, he can take a look."
    Kha "Sin embargo, si el Acechador [persistent.player_name] está interesado en algunas de mis otras mercancías, puede echar un vistazo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:379
translate spanish d18b_dcd1dd9f:

    # Z "I am not looking to buy. We are just looking around."
    Z "No estoy buscando comprar. Solo estamos mirando."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:382
translate spanish d18b_20a1df74:

    # Kha "I find that my best sales begin that way, but I can see that you would be a busy man already."
    Kha "Mis mejores ventas suelen empezar así, pero puedo ver que ya eres un hombre bastante ocupado."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:385
translate spanish d18b_64a81c4b:

    # Kha "Feel free to inspect the goods regardless, perhaps it will change your mind."
    Kha "Siéntete libre de inspeccionar la mercancía de todos modos, quizá cambies de opinión."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:386
translate spanish d18b_ebfeb02b:

    # Kha "Some fine goods on offer today, ranging from former tribeswoman to homebred slave."
    Kha "Hoy hay buenas ofertas: desde mujeres de antiguas tribus hasta esclavas nacidas en casa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:389
translate spanish d18b_d91904c6:

    # Kha "I suppose you're not interested in the man among them, so ignore that one."
    Kha "Supongo que no te interesa el hombre entre ellas, así que ignóralo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:393
translate spanish d18b_4f00042e:

    # "A familiar figure appears next to you..."
    "Una figura familiar aparece a tu lado..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:396
translate spanish d18b_7e127fd4:

    # Kha "Perhaps this fair lady is, though?"
    Kha "Aunque quizá a esta bella dama sí le interese, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:397
translate spanish d18b_8df9330b:

    # Kha "Looking for another toy, Savana?"
    Kha "¿Buscas otro juguete, Savana?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:401
translate spanish d18b_0c1a39c2:

    # Wom "Don't overinterpret it, Khalil. I'm just a curious girl."
    Wom "No exageres, Khalil. Solo soy una chica curiosa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:402
translate spanish d18b_dd51b4b4:

    # Wom "Tell me, what am I looking at...?"
    Wom "Dime, ¿qué estoy mirando...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:404
translate spanish d18b_8e212205:

    # Sav "Don't overinterpret it, Khalil. I'm just a curious girl."
    Sav "No exageres, Khalil. Solo soy una chica curiosa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:405
translate spanish d18b_766807f8:

    # Sav "Tell me, what am I looking at...?"
    Sav "Dime, ¿qué estoy mirando...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:404
translate spanish d18b_8d0bc929:

    # Kha "What you're seeing is all there is to know."
    Kha "Lo que ves es todo lo que hay que saber."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:407
translate spanish d18b_f3573538:

    # Kha "A worthless wastelander, capable enough for menial work. He survived our raid when his village was occupied by tribesmen and we liberated it."
    Kha "Un inútil del páramo, lo bastante capaz para trabajos de poca monta. Sobrevivió a nuestra incursión cuando su aldea fue ocupada por tribus y nosotros la liberamos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:408
translate spanish d18b_e26a057a:

    # Kha "My men took him in and trained him. He's not allowed to blink if I don't tell him to."
    Kha "Mis hombres lo recogieron y lo entrenaron. No se le permite ni parpadear si yo no se lo ordeno."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:411
translate spanish d18b_ed247168:

    # Kha "I figured a young male like him might be of use to a Lady in this city. If not, he will go back to the quarries."
    Kha "Pensé que un joven como él podría serle útil a alguna dama de esta ciudad. Si no, volverá a las canteras."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:412
translate spanish d18b_d26a8067:

    # Kha "Twenty gold for this one, for one year. But for you, I'll make it half, and I'm cutting my own throat."
    Kha "Veinte monedas de oro por un año. Pero para ti, te lo dejo a la mitad, ¡y casi me corto el cuello haciéndolo!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:420
translate spanish d18b_fa333988:

    # Wom "And what's the catch, old man?"
    Wom "¿Y cuál es la trampa, viejo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:415
translate spanish d18b_cd2ec0f3:

    # Sav "And what's the catch, old man?"
    Sav "¿Y cuál es la trampa, viejo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:418
translate spanish d18b_a11c1ec0:

    # Kha "You offend me, woman."
    Kha "Me ofendes, mujer."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:419
translate spanish d18b_9f61260b:

    # "From his businesslike manner, you can tell that the man is not really offended. He's merely preparing himself to haggle, like any merchant would."
    "Por su actitud de negociante, puedes ver que en realidad no está ofendido. Solo se está preparando para regatear, como cualquier mercader."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:420
translate spanish d18b_bb31b5c9:

    # Kha "Pay me a visit again, and we'll talk about what I can do for you. It has been too long since our last... encounter."
    Kha "Pásate a verme otro día y hablaremos de lo que puedo ofrecerte. Hace demasiado tiempo desde nuestro último... encuentro."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:431
translate spanish d18b_440d1c02:

    # Sav "Eh... not today, Khalil."
    Sav "Eh... hoy no, Khalil."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:432
translate spanish d18b_8e45af5f:

    # Sav "Try another time, perhaps you'll be luckier."
    Sav "Prueba otro día, quizás tengas más suerte."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:435
translate spanish d18b_a26e8a59:

    # "she leaves, unimpressed..."
    "ella se va, sin inmutarse..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:423
translate spanish d18b_ea9bc5ae:

    # Sav "{i}*sigh*{/i} Not today, Khalil."
    Sav "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Hoy no, Khalil."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:443
translate spanish d18b_e972fd7f:

    # Sav "Interesting to see you two here, of all places?"
    Sav "¿Qué interesante veros aquí, de todos los lugares?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:429
translate spanish d18b_7715e9db:

    # Z "I could say the same. Looking for some fun without your man?"
    Z "Podría decir lo mismo. ¿Buscando algo de diversión sin tu hombre?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:432
translate spanish d18b_6e189f80:

    # Sav "Oh... don't get the wrong idea. He knows I like to play, but where would the fun be if he wasn't there."
    Sav "Oh... no te equivoques. Él sabe que me gusta jugar, pero... ¿dónde estaría la gracia si no estuviera también presente?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:435
translate spanish d18b_ccb29bd0:

    # Sav "[A] is quite the looker. She's turning a lot of heads here, today."
    Sav "[A] es todo un bombón. Está llamando mucho la atención hoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:438
translate spanish d18b_c5a162b1:

    # Sav "...but with such a strong man at her side, I'm sure people won't dare to stare for long..."
    Sav "... pero con un hombre tan fuerte a su lado, seguro que no se atreven a mirar demasiado..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:441
translate spanish d18b_29716305:

    # "She looks at you with a hint of malice... is she testing you?"
    "Ella te mira con un deje de malicia... ¿te está poniendo a prueba?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:445
translate spanish d18b_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:448
translate spanish d18b_98c30faa:

    # Sav "Hm...?"
    Sav "¿Hm...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:449
translate spanish d18b_3b9a8763:

    # "You wrap your arm around her exposed hips and pull her towards you..."
    "Rodeas su cintura expuesta con el brazo y la acercas hacia ti..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:452
translate spanish d18b_dc7c1ed3:

    # Sav "That's very forward of you, manhandling me like that."
    Sav "Eso ha sido muy atrevido por tu parte, manosearme así."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:453
translate spanish d18b_c3f22c0b:

    # Sav "...what if Igor did the same with your wife?"
    Sav "... ¿y si Igor hiciera lo mismo con tu mujer?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:456
translate spanish d18b_0c61010d:

    # Z "Woman, are you going to pretend you were not flirting?"
    Z "Mujer, ¿vas a fingir que no estabas flirteando?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:457
translate spanish d18b_175b79cf:

    # Sav "That is fair. I was curious to see how you react..."
    Sav "Tienes razón. Solo quería ver cómo reaccionabas..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:458
translate spanish d18b_d03cbefe:

    # Sav "But my question stands: what if my man did the same to your woman?"
    Sav "Pero mi pregunta sigue en pie: ¿y si mi hombre hiciera lo mismo con tu mujer?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:459
translate spanish d18b_17318268:

    # Z "My woman would not provoke your man, if I did not tell her to."
    Z "Mi mujer no provocaría a tu hombre, si yo no se lo ordenara."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:460
translate spanish d18b_920fc511:

    # Sav "Well... I guess that's where [W] and I differ, and he knows that..."
    Sav "Bueno... supongo que ahí es donde [W] y yo diferimos, y él lo sabe..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:463
translate spanish d18b_b8195ae4:

    # Z "Igor knows what?"
    Z "¿Igor sabe qué?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:466
translate spanish d18b_8fbc153f:

    # Sav "I just told you. I am a curious girl... and I occasionally have my own adventures."
    Sav "Ya te lo he dicho. Soy una chica curiosa... y de vez en cuando tengo mis propias aventuras."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:469
translate spanish d18b_84d58464:

    # Sav "...it comes with benefits, even for him."
    Sav "... y eso también tiene beneficios, incluso para él."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:472
translate spanish d18b_8d0482ef:

    # "You already thought that it might be the case, but now you know for a fact that this woman is a free spirit, just like you."
    "Ya sospechabas que podía ser así, pero ahora sabes con certeza que esta mujer es un espíritu libre, igual que tú."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:473
translate spanish d18b_2c75ecd9:

    # "And just like you, she has the support of a loving partner in crime."
    "Y al igual que tú, cuenta con el apoyo de una pareja que la comprende."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:476
translate spanish d18b_9626b3ec:

    # Sav "Now, [A]... tell me, where is your [persistent.dad] leading you today?"
    Sav "Ahora, [A]... dime, ¿adónde te lleva hoy tu [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:477
translate spanish d18b_d7b78c65:

    # A "Oh... we are just grabbing a few supplies..."
    A "Oh... solo estamos comprando algunas cosas..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:478
translate spanish d18b_a3940862:

    # A "...my [persistent.mom] said that I should learn to take more responsibilities."
    A "... mi [persistent.mom] dijo que debería aprender a asumir más responsabilidades."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:479
translate spanish d18b_64c88ec3:

    # Sav "{i}*chuckles*{/i}... and is that all you're looking for today? Groceries?"
    Sav "{i}*risilla*{/i}... ¿y eso es todo lo que buscas hoy? ¿Víveres?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:480
translate spanish d18b_99b50aed:

    # A "I..."
    A "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:481
translate spanish d18b_b56c2cfe:

    # Sav "Don't get flustered... I think I know what you mean."
    Sav "No te pongas nerviosa... Creo que ya sé a qué te refieres."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:484
translate spanish d18b_a11e4478:

    # Sav "Well... Anyway... I am going to leave you two to it."
    Sav "Bueno... en fin... os voy a dejar tranquilos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:485
translate spanish d18b_02313a40:

    # Sav "It has been nice meeting you, but my man is going to come back tomorrow, and there are a lot of things to do before then."
    Sav "Ha sido un placer veros, pero mi hombre vuelve mañana, y hay muchas cosas que hacer antes de eso."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:488
translate spanish d18b_9bed6c93:

    # Sav "I was thinking, perhaps you and your wife would be interested in a double date?"
    Sav "Estaba pensando... quizá tú y tu esposa estaríais interesados en una ¿cita doble?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:489
translate spanish d18b_7b367b88:

    # Sav "Getting to know each other more can't hurt, can it?"
    Sav "Conocernos un poco más no puede hacer daño, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:492
translate spanish d18b_821e85ba:

    # Z "I will talk to my wife and we will let you know."
    Z "Hablaré con mi mujer y te diremos algo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:497
translate spanish d18b_143ff084:

    # Sav "Well... I am going to leave you two to it."
    Sav "Bueno... os dejo tranquilos entonces."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:498
translate spanish d18b_02313a40_1:

    # Sav "It has been nice meeting you, but my man is going to come back tomorrow, and there are a lot of things to do before then."
    Sav "Ha sido un placer veros, pero mi hombre vuelve mañana, y hay muchas cosas que hacer antes de eso."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:501
translate spanish d18b_1a3afa90:

    # Sav "I was thinking, perhaps you and your wife would be interested in grabbing dinner with Igor and me?"
    Sav "Estaba pensando, ¿quizás tú y tu mujer estaríais interesados en cenar con Igor y conmigo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:502
translate spanish d18b_7b367b88_1:

    # Sav "Getting to know each other more can't hurt, can it?"
    Sav "Conocernos un poco más no puede hacer daño, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:505
