    Ci2 "No puedo evitar notar cierto parecido entre esta esclava y la Dama de mi casa, aunque..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:770
translate spanish re_d18b83_0b1c2bc9:

    # Sl "Mh... {i}*sucking*{/i}"
    Sl "Mh... {i}*chupando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:771
translate spanish re_d18b83_0d2375c5:

    # Ci2 "Oh well, perhaps it's but a silly coincidence."
    Ci2 "En fin, quizá solo sea una coincidencia tonta."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:774
translate spanish re_d18b83_154fd15a:

    # Ci "I can't recall Lady Nour having any siblings."
    Ci "No recuerdo que Lady Nour tuviera hermanos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:775
translate spanish re_d18b83_d4209fc9:

    # Ci2 "No... no siblings, indeed."
    Ci2 "No... no tenía hermanos, efectivamente."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:778
translate spanish re_d18b83_568773e7:

    # "The young woman keeps sucking obediently..."
    "La joven sigue chupando obedientemente..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:779
translate spanish re_d18b83_4332b9a2:

    # Ci2 "I could be wrong, but I do recall a family feud a couple years ago..."
    Ci2 "Podría estar equivocado, pero recuerdo una disputa familiar hace un par de años..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:782
translate spanish re_d18b83_25f545c5:

    # Ci2 "Ah, what gives. In any case, this addition to the house should bring in some new blood."
    Ci2 "Bah, qué más da. En cualquier caso, esta nueva adquisición debería traer sangre fresca a la casa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:783
translate spanish re_d18b83_77c2e930:

    # Ci "She best give you a good heir, then!"
    Ci "¡Esperemos que te dé un buen heredero, entonces!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:791
translate spanish d18b93_4d8272fb:

    # Z "That really is not that unusual, [A]."
    Z "Eso no es tan raro, [A]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:795
translate spanish d18b93_368c3b40:

    # "You keep walking, and look around the place..."
    "Sigues caminando y observas el lugar..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:798
translate spanish d18b93_17528abb:

    # Ci "Hey..."
    Ci "Eh..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:799
translate spanish d18b93_15f876a0:

    # Ci "[A]? Is that you?"
    Ci "[A], ¿eres tú?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:802
translate spanish d18b93_8f79c22d:

    # A "R... Rami?!"
    A "R... ¿Rami?!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:805
translate spanish d18b93_3ea5e6bb:

    # "[A] stops in her tracks and stares in surprise..."
    "[A] se detiene en seco, mirándolo sorprendida..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:808
translate spanish d18b93_da29acda:

    # Ram "[A]! Fancy meeting you here..!"
    Ram "¡[A]! ¡Qué coincidencia encontrarte aquí...!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:811
translate spanish d18b93_934ee30a:

    # Ram "I was just on my way to the academy. It's good to see you."
    Ram "Iba de camino a la academia. Me alegra verte."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:814
translate spanish d18b93_5a939197:

    # A "I didn't know you would become a..."
    A "No sabía que te habías convertido en..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:817
translate spanish d18b93_ffb93450:

    # Ram "Oh... apologies!"
    Ram "Oh... ¡perdón!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:820
translate spanish d18b93_2860c0a8:

    # Ram "S-sir, I mean, Stalker [persistent.player_name], please allow me to introduce myself."
    Ram "S-señor, quiero decir, Acechador [persistent.player_name], permítame presentarme."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:821
translate spanish d18b93_bfcef8d4:

    # Ram "My name is Rami. I am enrolled in the Academy and preparing to become a Stalker. At least that's my goal."
    Ram "Me llamo Rami. Estoy inscrito en la Academia y me preparo para convertirme en Acechador. Al menos, ese es mi objetivo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:822
translate spanish d18b93_697174e3:

    # Ram "I know your [persistent.da] from when we attended basic education together."
    Ram "Conozco a su [persistent.da] de cuando asistimos juntos a la educación básica."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:827
translate spanish d18b93_cc839ec9:

    # Z "Well met, Rami."
    Z "Un placer, Rami."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:833
translate spanish d18b93_e2100fc1:

    # "To ignore Zetan customs and not first address the head of the House is bad form..."
    "Ignorar las costumbres zetanas y no dirigirse primero al jefe de la Casa es de mala educación..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:834
translate spanish d18b93_41b60685:

    # Z "You realise that you should have addressed me first, don't you?"
    Z "Te das cuenta de que deberías haberte dirigido a mí primero, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:837
translate spanish d18b93_f757f857:

    # Ram "I... apologise, Sir. That won't happen again! I just... I was caught by surprise."
    Ram "L-lo... siento, señor. ¡No volverá a pasar! Es solo que... me cogió por sorpresa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:841
translate spanish d18b93_265db6db:

    # Z "My [persistent.da] never told me she knew another Stalker."
    Z "Mi [persistent.da] nunca me dijo que conocía a otro Acechador."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:842
translate spanish d18b93_7ce224d3:

    # A "I didn't know either, [persistent.dad]..."
    A "Yo tampoco lo sabía, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:845
translate spanish d18b93_ef8d2080:

    # Ram "That is because I finally got the nerve to join the Academy only after we completed our basic education. Late, I suppose."
    Ram "Eso es porque solo tuve el valor de unirme a la Academia después de terminar la educación básica. Algo tarde, supongo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:848
translate spanish d18b93_73dc8707:

    # Z "You knew my name. Why is that?"
    Z "Sabías mi nombre. ¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:851
translate spanish d18b93_77c78d3c:

    # Ram "Well, When we were little, it was no secret that [A]'s father was a Stalker and, well, the stories about Stalkers are exciting!"
    Ram "Bueno... cuando éramos pequeños, no era un secreto que el padre de [A] era un Acechador y, bueno... ¡las historias sobre los Acechadores siempre emocionaban!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:852
translate spanish d18b93_16c356f4:

    # Ram "Even without the desire to become one myself, what kid doesn't like to hear about adventures and great fighters?"
    Ram "Incluso sin querer ser uno, ¿qué niño no disfruta escuchando aventuras y relatos de grandes luchadores?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:853
translate spanish d18b93_c68922f4:

    # Ram "Since then, I have been reading up on your accomplishments, and have asked around. You're one of the most famous Stalkers in activity."
    Ram "Desde entonces he leído sobre tus logros y he preguntado por ti. Eres uno de los Acechadores más famosos en activo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:856
translate spanish d18b93_626b61f3:

    # Z "Still, there are others, so... why me specifically? Be honest."
    Z "Aun así, hay otros... ¿por qué yo, específicamente? Sé honesto."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:859
translate spanish d18b93_7b4e43c6:

    # Ram "Oh... It's... ahem..."
    Ram "Oh... Es... ejem..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:860
translate spanish d18b93_7a4729b1:

    # Ram "Well... You're a bit of a hero of the City, and, well... Thanks to [A], yours were the first stories I learned about."
    Ram "Bueno... eres algo así como un héroe en la ciudad y, bueno... gracias a [A], tus historias fueron las primeras que escuché."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:861
translate spanish d18b93_c5413018:

    # Ram "Also... "
    Ram "Además..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:862
translate spanish d18b93_1a9c7421:

    # "You can tell he's hesitating, as he looks from you to [A] and back."
    "Notas que duda, mirando de ti a [A] y viceversa."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:863
translate spanish d18b93_4dd50889:

    # Ram "The truth is... I might have had a crush on [A], when we were young..."
    Ram "La verdad es... que puede que tuviera un pequeño flechazo con [A] cuando éramos jovenes..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:864
translate spanish d18b93_c1992dc6:

    # A "...!"
    A "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:865
translate spanish d18b93_6ff194f7:

    # Ram "I mean... She's part of why I want to become a Stalker. How else could I measure up?"
    Ram "Quiero decir... Ella es parte de la razón por la que quiero ser Acechador. ¿Cómo iba a estar a su altura si no?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:866
translate spanish d18b93_55345e50:

    # Ram "I still could not think of anyone I like more."
    Ram "Todavía no creo haber conocido a nadie que me guste más."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:869
translate spanish d18b93_3ea0547c:

    # "[A] looks aside, waiting for your reaction..."
    "[A] aparta la mirada, esperando tu reacción..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:874
translate spanish d18b93_97e1b240:

    # Z "If you like her so much, then what exactly is it you like about her?"
    Z "Si tanto te gusta, ¿qué es exactamente lo que te gusta de ella?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:877
translate spanish d18b93_ca20d2b9:

    # Ram "[A] is... well... where do I start?"
    Ram "[A] es... bueno... ¿por dónde empiezo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:882
translate spanish d18b93_921c2a8c:

    # Z "You're not the first to admire her. I hope you know that."
    Z "No eres el primero que la admira. Espero que lo sepas."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:885
translate spanish d18b93_2894c325:

    # Ram "Yes, sir... She has many admirers, always did..."
    Ram "Sí, señor... Siempre ha tenido muchos admiradores..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:886
translate spanish d18b93_3c21cba5:

    # Z "Let me hear why *you* admire her."
    Z "Déjame oír por qué *tú* la admiras."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:887
translate spanish d18b93_2b8a6b00:

    # Ram "Yes, sir."
    Ram "Sí, señor."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:891
translate spanish d18b101_9774c632:

    # Z "What makes you think I will hand her out?"
    Z "¿Qué te hace pensar que te la voy a entregar?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:894
translate spanish d18b101_5ed4cd8a:

    # Ram "I..."
    Ram "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:895
translate spanish d18b101_862244e6:

    # "You see him focusing a second, before anwering in as neutral a tone as he can muster."
    "Lo ves concentrarse un segundo antes de responder con el tono más neutro que consigue."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:896
translate spanish d18b101_edce0950:

    # Ram "I would not presume that, Sir. That's why I want to make a name for myself, become a well respected Stalker like yourself."
    Ram "No lo presupongo, señor. Por eso quiero hacerme un nombre, convertirme en un Acechador respetado como usted."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:897
translate spanish d18b101_131cfad9:

    # Ram "Then, maybe, in time..."
    Ram "Y entonces, quizá, con el tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:900
translate spanish d18b101_264112c6:

    # Ram "I am not blind, Sir, and I know beauty when I see it, but that is not what draws me to her."
    Ram "No soy ciego, señor, sé reconocer la belleza cuando la veo, pero no es eso lo que más me atrae de ella."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:901
translate spanish d18b101_11e153e4:

    # Ram "Yes, she is a very attractive woman, but what I value most about her is her character."
    Ram "Sí, es una mujer muy atractiva, pero lo que más valoro es su carácter."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:902
translate spanish d18b101_7a56b711:

    # Ram "I love her spontaneous cheerfulness, but I could always see that she was proud, and mature..."
    Ram "Amo su alegría espontánea, pero siempre vi que era orgullosa y madura..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:903
translate spanish d18b101_f7d7c41f:

    # Ram "She always knew her worth, even back then."
    Ram "Siempre supo lo que valía, incluso entonces."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:904
translate spanish d18b101_b1fef26b:

    # Ram "...and while we were never close, I hope you remember me in a similar way, [A]."
    Ram "... y aunque nunca fuimos cercanos, espero que me recuerdes de una forma parecida, [A]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:906
translate spanish d18b108_c8b2062a:

    # Ram "Anyway... I... am glad to have met you again and to have had the chance to formally introduce myself."
    Ram "De todas formas... me alegro de haberte vuelto a ver y de haber podido presentarme formalmente."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:907
translate spanish d18b108_7364e171:

    # Ram "I hope you will give me the chance to see your [persistent.da] again."
    Ram "Espero que me des la oportunidad de volver a ver a tu [persistent.da]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:910
translate spanish d18b108_9b036cd6:

    # "You put your hand around her..."
    "Pones tu mano sobre ella..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:912
translate spanish d18b108_1c719f1c:

    # Z "Don't expect to see her again."
    Z "No esperes volver a verla."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:914
translate spanish d18b108_491b6c91:

    # Z "I will think about whether you will see her again or not."
    Z "Ya decidiré si la verás de nuevo o no."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:917
translate spanish d18b108_3a62790e:

    # Z "Until I decide, you would do well not to let me catch you sniffing around her..."
    Z "Hasta que yo decida, más te vale que no te vea rondándola..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:921
translate spanish d18b108_a0709ed9:

    # Ram "Y-yes, Stalker. Please know that it was not my intend to harass [A] in any way."
    Ram "S-sí, Acechador. Por favor, sepa que no fue mi intención molestar a [A] de ninguna manera."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:923
translate spanish d18b108_36982c80:

    # Ram "S-Stalker [persistent.player_name]... I will await your decision, and give you my word to not contact or harass [A] in any way."
    Ram "A-Acechador [persistent.player_name]... Esperaré su decisión, y le doy mi palabra de que no contactaré ni molestaré a [A] de ninguna forma."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:926
translate spanish d18b108_f5bf48a8:

    # "You look at the boy who just asked to date your [persistent.da]."
    "Miras al chico que acaba de pedirte permiso para cortejar a tu [persistent.da]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:927
translate spanish d18b108_bd745200:

    # "He looks around her age, seems to be in good shape and to make an effort to be presentable."
    "Parece de su misma edad, en buena forma, y se esfuerza por ser presentable."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:928
translate spanish d18b108_807bd290:

    # "Despite his clumsy introduction, he seems to be a respectful young man."
    "Pese a su torpe presentación, parece un joven respetuoso."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:929
translate spanish d18b108_947e977a:

    # Z "You're expected at the academy?"
    Z "¿Se supone que tienes que estar en la academia ahora?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:932
translate spanish d18b108_c052cf7e:

    # Ram "Yes, sir. My Master is most likely going to scold me for being late, but I couldn't let this opportunity go to waste!"
    Ram "Sí, señor. Seguramente mi maestro me regañará por llegar tarde, ¡pero no podía desperdiciar esta oportunidad!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:935
translate spanish d18b108_f8434482:

    # Z "You should run, then."
    Z "Deberías correr, entonces."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:938
translate spanish d18b108_2421d657:

    # Ram "I shall. Stalker [persistent.player_name], [A], it was a great pleasure to meet you again."
    Ram "Así lo haré. Acechador [persistent.player_name], [A], ha sido un gran placer volver a veros."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:943
translate spanish d18b108_54be703f:

    # "He hurries away..."
    "Se aleja corriendo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:946
translate spanish d18b108_2ea74c97:

    # A "[persistent.dad!c]...?"
    A "¿[persistent.dad!c]...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:947
translate spanish d18b108_1fc04d1c:

    # A "I know I never told you about him..."
    A "Sé que nunca te hablé de él..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:950
translate spanish d18b108_5dcc3c95:

    # Z "You didn't."
    Z "No lo hiciste."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:953
translate spanish d18b108_21c040bd:

    # A "But... there wasn't really anything to talk about!"
    A "Pero... ¡realmente no había nada de qué hablar!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:956
translate spanish d18b108_d64e7b86:

    # "She looks aside, thinking..."
    "Frunce la nariz, pensativa..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:959
translate spanish d18b108_245ebefe:

    # A "I haven't thought of him at all until just now."
    A "Ni siquiera había pensado en él hasta hoy."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:960
translate spanish d18b108_5df4a0f6:

    # A "He was such an outcast back in school, a bit of a loner. I figured he would end up either at the Temple or apprenticed with some trader."
    A "Era un marginado en el colegio, un solitario. Pensaba que acabaría en el Templo o como aprendiz de algún comerciante."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:963
translate spanish d18b108_5430ade9:

    # A "But now he's training to become a Stalker, and says he loves me? That's weird!"
    A "Pero ahora entrena para ser Acechador... ¿y dice que me ama? ¡Qué raro!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:966
translate spanish d18b108_750be657:

    # Z "You didn't expect it?"
    Z "¿No te lo esperabas?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:969
translate spanish d18b108_9757d628:

    # A "No, I told you. We shared classes and he was a kind boy. I had to think real hard to remember his name."
    A "No, te lo he dicho. Compartíamos clases, era un chico amable. Tuve que esforzarme para recordar su nombre."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:970
translate spanish d18b108_2633655a:

    # A "That's about it. I am confused, [persistent.dad]... really!"
    A "Eso es todo. Estoy confundida, [persistent.dad]... ¡de verdad!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:973
translate spanish d18b108_cb8bc2fc:

    # Z "Let's talk about this another time, then."
    Z "Hablaremos de esto otro día."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:976
translate spanish d18b108_33d0c05a:

    # A "You're right... today is about us, anyway!"
    A "Tienes razón... ¡hoy es nuestro día!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:979
translate spanish d18b108_ca465e88:

    # A "... I have been... waiting for another day like last time, [persistent.dad]..."
    A "... He estado... esperando otro día como el de la última vez, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:982
translate spanish d18b108_1411919a:

    # "She puts her arms together shily..."
    "Ella junta tímidamente los brazos..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:983
translate spanish d18b108_88a5d808:

    # Z "Let's go, then."
    Z "Vamos entonces."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:986
translate spanish d18b108_331801e8:

    # "You take a few steps, before you hear yet another interruption..."
    "Das unos pasos cuando escuchas otra interrupción..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:987
translate spanish d18b108_d619b913:

    # Ci "Hello, sir! You there!"
    Ci "¡Hola, señor! ¡Usted! ¡Un momento, por favor!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:990
translate spanish d18b108_98e45194:

    # Ci "A moment of your time, please?"
    Ci "¿Un momento de su tiempo, por favor?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:993
translate spanish d18b108_a8ce84a7:

    # Ci "Would you have a look please?"
    Ci "¿Tendría la amabilidad de echar un vistazo?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:996
translate spanish d18b108_47451dec:

    # Ci "Her services are cheap, Sir! Cleaning, dusting, dancing, fucking, all for a few coppers!"
    Ci "¡Sus servicios son baratos, señor! Limpiar, quitar el polvo, bailar, follar, ¡todo por unas pocas monedas!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:999
translate spanish d18b108_036bd79f:

    # Slw "Bastard..."
    Slw "Bastardo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1002
translate spanish d18b108_04b51351:

    # A "That's an odd way to sell your wares, isn't it?"
    A "Vaya forma rara de vender su mercancía, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1003
translate spanish d18b108_bd6e51be:

    # A "Do you want to see more, [persistent.dad]?"
    A "¿Quieres ver más, [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1006
translate spanish d18b108_b87edf97:

    # Z "Let's see what he really has to offer..."
    Z "Veamos qué ofrece realmente..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1009
translate spanish d18b108_7f14fa74:

    # "You approach the young man..."
    "Te acercas al joven..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1012
translate spanish d18b108_572a9d93:

    # Ci "Sir, thank you for approaching. Blessing on you, sir."
    Ci "Señor, gracias por acercarse. ¡Que los dioses lo bendigan, señor!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1015
translate spanish d18b108_73b51876:

    # Ci "Please, have a look at the merchandise!"
    Ci "Por favor, eche un vistazo a la mercancía."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1018
translate spanish d18b108_8f10de02:

    # Sl "Your merchandise... Can't even call me your sister anymore?"
    Sl "¿Tu mercancía...? ¿Ya ni siquiera puedes llamarme hermana?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1021
translate spanish d18b108_f84907a2:

    # Sl "Was ruining the name of the family not enough? Did you have to reduce me to a common slave?"
    Sl "¿No fue suficiente con arruinar el nombre de la familia? ¿También tenías que rebajarme a esclava común?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1024
translate spanish d18b108_61298cba:

    # "The young man grunts, frustrated by the woman's words..."
    "El joven gruñe, frustrado por las palabras de la mujer..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1027
translate spanish d18b108_f4777925:

    # Ci "I... apologize for my twin sister's bad conduct, sir. She has a hard time adjusting to her new circumstances..."
    Ci "Yo... pido disculpas por la mala conducta de mi hermana gemela, señor. Le cuesta adaptarse a su nueva situación..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1030
translate spanish d18b108_0f064e31:

    # Ci "But yes, I can't deny that we are in a tough financial situation ever since our parents' passing."
    Ci "Pero no puedo negar que estamos pasando por una situación financiera muy difícil desde la muerte de nuestros padres."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:1031
translate spanish d18b108_a5c20e1a:

