    # A "Uhm... [persistent.mom]...?"
    A "Uhm... ¿[persistent.mom]...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4742
translate spanish d18e_1562bd6b:

    # A "What is happening?"
    A "¿Qué está pasando?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4745
translate spanish d18e_aacd0f38:

    # W "We are graced by the presence of the highest born, [A]. Such a blessing! Go inform your [persistent.dad] that his Queen is in attendance..."
    W "Estamos siendo bendecidos con la presencia de la de más alta nobleza, [A]. ¡Qué bendición! Ve a informar a tu [persistent.dad] que su Reina está presente..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4748
translate spanish d18e_f2c5b136:

    # A "O-okay. I will go immediately!"
    A "¡O-okay! ¡Iré de inmediato!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4753
translate spanish d18e_9f43e529:

    # "She hurries inside..."
    "Ella se apresura a entrar..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4757
translate spanish d18e_412b5ee9:

    # W "My [persistent.da]. She is young and impressionable. Not too far from your age, I believe."
    W "Mi [persistent.da]. Ella es joven e impresionable. No muy lejos de tu edad, creo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4759
translate spanish d18e_73d94568:

    # W "She is young and impressionable. Not too far from your age, I believe."
    W "Ella es joven e impresionable. No muy lejos de tu edad, creo."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4762
translate spanish d18e_b370bb5c:

    # Q "I'm sure it's easy to be impressed, when one's experience of the world is so limited."
    Q "Seguro que es fácil impresionarse, cuando la experiencia de uno en el mundo es tan limitada."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4765
translate spanish d18e_3d079977:

    # Q "Wasn't she the one who got into trouble by merely walking around the market?"
    Q "¿No fue ella la que se metió en problemas por simplemente caminar por el mercado?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4768
translate spanish d18e_8177ee9f:

    # W "I guess that's to be expected, The world is such an unsafe place. Zeta too, sometimes."
    W "Supongo que eso es de esperarse, cuando los gobernantes de la ciudad no pueden controlar a su población."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4771
translate spanish d18e_750fb527:

    # "You approach, barely able to make out what they're talking about..."
    "Te acercas, apenas pudiendo distinguir de qué están hablando..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4774
translate spanish d18e_62686e53:

    # Z "The Queen of Zeta, visiting my humble abode?"
    Z "¿La Reina de Zeta, visitando mi humilde morada?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4775
translate spanish d18e_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4778
translate spanish d18e_27f7d9be:

    # "You step behind [W], wrapping her in an embrace..."
    "Te pones detrás de [W], rodeándola con un abrazo..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4779
translate spanish d18e_ef089ca0:

    # Z "Is everything well, my dear?"
    Z "¿Está todo bien, querida?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4780
translate spanish d18e_3268034e:

    # W "It is now..."
    W "Ahora lo está..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4783
translate spanish d18e_f6ac3960:

    # Z "Tell me, what did I miss?"
    Z "Dime, ¿qué me he perdido?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4786
translate spanish d18e_517837e7:

    # W "It seems that our young Queen wishes to see our household. Perhaps she wants to stay for dinner, too?"
    W "Parece que nuestra joven Reina desea ver nuestra casa. ¿Tal vez quiera quedarse a cenar también?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4789
translate spanish d18e_c34f353e:

    # W "Hm?"
    W "¿Hm?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4792
translate spanish d18e_084c8540:

    # Q "Pfft..."
    Q "Pfft..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4795
translate spanish d18e_e17af359:

    # Q "As if I would ever..!"
    Q "¡Como si yo fuera a hacer algo así...!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4796
translate spanish d18e_25156a97:

    # Q "I am reviewing the outposts of the city. Your place happened to be en route and I wanted to see how you spend my money."
    Q "Estoy revisando los puestos de avanzada de la ciudad. Tu lugar estaba en ruta y quería ver cómo gastas mi dinero."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4799
translate spanish d18e_4c6243e1:

    # W "Is that so, my Queen?"
    W "¿Es eso así, mi Reina?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4802
translate spanish d18e_473a13d8:

    # "She steps back..."
    "Ella da un paso atrás..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4805
translate spanish d18e_a55dec36:

    # Q "Stalker, I think I pay you too much, by the looks of it. I should at least make you earn it properly."
    Q "Acechador, creo que te pago demasiado, por lo que parece. Debería al menos hacer que lo ganes de manera adecuada."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4806
translate spanish d18e_fb232d05:

    # Q "You will come to the palace, tonight. I have need of your services."
    Q "Vendrás al palacio esta noche. Necesito tus servicios."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4809
translate spanish d18e_16e65e3e:

    # Q "I would say I am sorry for ruining your plans for this evening..."
    Q "Diría que lo siento por arruinar tus planes para esta noche..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4812
translate spanish d18e_da32005b:

    # Q "...but I suppose your wife could use the rest. At her age, it must be difficult to have to deal with a man of your vigor."
    Q "...pero supongo que tu esposa podría necesitar el descanso. A su edad, debe ser difícil tener que lidiar con un hombre de tu vigor."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4815
translate spanish d18e_54b5c77e:

    # Q "Guards, move out. We still have places to be."
    Q "Guardias, en marcha. Aún tenemos lugares a los que ir."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4818
translate spanish d18e_d60ab63c:

    # G "Y-yes, my Queen."
    G "S-sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4821
translate spanish d18e_f0281db7:

    # Q "Don't take long, Stalker [persistent.player_name]. The sun will set soon."
    Q "No tardes, Acechador [persistent.player_name]. El sol se pondrá pronto."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4824
translate spanish d18e_e254e38d:

    # "She seems ready to move to her next commitment, but stops in her tracks."
    "Ella parece dispuesta a pasar a su siguiente compromiso, pero se detiene en seco."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4825
translate spanish d18e_04f5b2ec:

    # Q "Your other [persistent.da] is a pretty little thing."
    Q "Tu otra [persistent.da] es una cosita bastante bonita."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4828
translate spanish d18e_39e4010c:

    # Q "Maybe I should have her join the Royal service. I am sure the guards would find a use for her."
    Q "Tal vez debería hacerla unirse al servicio Real. Estoy segura de que los guardias encontrarían una forma de usarla."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4830
translate spanish d18e_dfd7c5bb:

    # Q "Maybe her [persistent.dad] should think about that, before neglecting or... interpreting my wishes as he sees fit."
    Q "Tal vez su [persistent.dad] debería pensar en eso, antes de descuidar o... interpretar mis deseos como le plazca."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4832
translate spanish d18e_742e2e8d:

    # Q "Maybe Stalker [persistent.player_name] should think about that, before neglecting or... interpreting my wishes as he sees fit."
    Q "Tal vez el Acechador [persistent.player_name] debería pensar en eso, antes de descuidar o... interpretar mis deseos como le plazca."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4835
translate spanish d18e_f5264709:

    # Q "Let's ride."
    Q "Montemos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4836
translate spanish d18e_0b50c580:

    # G "Yes, my Queen."
    G "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4837
translate spanish d18e_c2c9cc07_1:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4842
translate spanish d18e_dd05e5a8:

    # "The guards walk in formation around her camel as she rides off.. A larger platoon that had remained out of sight joins them."
    "Los guardias caminan en formación alrededor de su camello mientras ella se aleja... Un pelotón más grande que se había mantenido fuera de vista se une a ellos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4845
translate spanish d18e_a82ce7ad:

    # "Having closed the gate, your wife pauses..."
    "Habiendo cerrado la puerta, tu esposa hace una pausa..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4846
translate spanish d18e_502630de:

    # W "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    W "{i}*suspiros*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4847
translate spanish d18e_6e037dd7:

    # Z "...?"
    Z "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4848
translate spanish d18e_e181103e:

    # Z "[W]?"
    Z "¿[W]?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4852
translate spanish d18e_b17d7607:

    # W "{i}*chuckles*{/i}"
    W "{i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4856
translate spanish d18e_2465c993:

    # "She starts laughing out loud, but suppresses it quickly..."
    "Ella comienza a reírse en voz alta, pero lo suprime rápidamente..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4859
translate spanish d18e_5ca22365:

    # "...and turns around to face you..."
    "... y se da la vuelta para mirarte..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4862
translate spanish d18e_972bf5ea:

    # W "Is she always this... feisty?"
    W "¿Es siempre así de... rebelde?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4865
translate spanish d18e_30dd78bf:

    # Z "I... wouldn't say so."
    Z "No... no diría eso."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4868
translate spanish d18e_55e5d458:

    # W "{i}*sigh*{/i} of course..."
    W "{i}*suspiros*{/i} por supuesto..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4871
translate spanish d18e_fde18620:

    # Z "What?"
    Z "¿Qué?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4874
translate spanish d18e_9b5006dc:

    # "She turns her back to you, raising her arms theatrically, laughing in the process..."
    "Ella te da la espalda, levantando los brazos de forma teatral, riendo mientras lo hace..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4877
translate spanish d18e_6c1137cd:

    # W "The mighty Merneith!"
    W "¡La poderosa Merneith!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4880
translate spanish d18e_040b322e:

    # W "...Holy Queen of our beloved Zeta!"
    W "... ¡Santa Reina de nuestra amada Zeta!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4883
translate spanish d18e_e502ef7b:

    # W "True Goddess-child of Ra..."
    W "Verdadera hija de la diosa Ra..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4886
translate spanish d18e_9e98befd:

    # W "Bearer of the light of civilisation..."
    W "Portadora de la luz de la civilización..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4889
translate spanish d18e_0a98374b:

    # W "...has a crush on my husband!"
    W "... ¡está enamorada de mi marido!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4890
translate spanish d18e_7476c53c:

    # W "{i}*laughs*{/i}"
    W "{i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4893
translate spanish d18e_f6a16b8a:

    # W "Well, husband. Turns out you weren't wrong when you said you were making progress."
    W "Bueno, marido. Resulta que no estabas equivocado cuando dijiste que estabas haciendo progresos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4894
translate spanish d18e_0aeccc11:

    # W "It looks like you will be needed for another close audience with the Queen."
    W "Parece que necesitarás una nueva audiencia cercana con la Reina."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4897
translate spanish d18e_321d63ea:

    # Z "You said it yourself, mighty Merneith..."
    Z "Lo dijiste tú misma, poderosa Merneith..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4900
translate spanish d18e_15cab1e3:

    # W "Well then... we're old enough to know what might happen next, aren't we?"
    W "Bueno entonces... ya somos lo suficientemente grandes como para saber lo que podría pasar a continuación, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4903
translate spanish d18e_9882a21b:

    # W "A dangerous game to play, perhaps, but the possible rewards..."
    W "Un juego peligroso, tal vez, pero las posibles recompensas..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4907
translate spanish d18e_9aaab0be:

    # W "If you decide to go for it, perhaps you want to make her pay for how she treated me just now."
    W "Si decides ir por ello, tal vez quieras hacerla pagar por cómo me trató hace un momento."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4910
translate spanish d18e_3623a20a:

    # Z "She certainly wasn't happy after what happened last time."
    Z "Ciertamente no estaba contenta después de lo que pasó la última vez."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4913
translate spanish d18e_6e60b551:

    # W "Well... I trust your instincts will tell you how to move forward."
    W "Bueno... confío en que tus instintos te dirán cómo seguir adelante."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4914
translate spanish d18e_d861ee35:

    # W "You have a Queen to conquer, husband. You should prepare..."
    W "Tienes una Reina que conquistar, marido. Deberías prepararte..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4917
translate spanish d18e_bbf601cd:

    # W "All I ask of you is to make it back in one piece. The rest... we can talk about later."
    W "Todo lo que te pido es que regreses entero. Lo demás... podemos hablarlo después."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4926
translate spanish d18f_4d68a76b:

    # "An hour passes and you eventually head to the city."
    "Pasa una hora y finalmente te diriges a la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4927
translate spanish d18f_96f84aa5:

    # "Upon arrival at the palace, you are quickly ushered to the throne room, where the Queen is waiting for you..."
    "Al llegar al palacio, te conducen rápidamente a la sala del trono, donde la Reina te espera..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4931
translate spanish d18f_bba1a14c:

    # Q "Stalker! You have arrived, finally!"
    Q "¡Acechador! ¡Has llegado, por fin!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4932
translate spanish d18f_f0c80740:

    # Q "Did my personal summons not seem important enough?"
    Q "¿No parecía suficientemente importante mi convocatoria personal?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4935
translate spanish d18f_5fe59247:

    # "Not having had any indication of real urgency, you wait to see what the reason of her anger is."
    "Al no tener ningún indicio de verdadera urgencia, esperas a ver cuál es el motivo de su enfado."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4936
translate spanish d18f_b47bb645:

    # Q "You forget yourself, Stalker. Kneel for your queen!"
    Q "Olvidas quién eres, Acechador. ¡Arrodíllate ante tu reina!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4939
translate spanish d18f_02210b2a:

    # Z "You want me to kneel?"
    Z "¿Quieres que me arrodille?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4942
translate spanish d18f_e7b11d79:

    # G "Stalker... be warned. We will not tolerate your games again."
    G "Acechador... ten cuidado. No toleraremos tus juegos otra vez."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4943
translate spanish d18f_2baafecf:

    # G "Take a knee!"
    G "¡Arrodíllate!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4946
translate spanish d18f_d3ca1214:

    # G "Well done..."
    G "Bien hecho..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4949
translate spanish d18f_d51ba3f9:

    # "Seeing as there is no other option, you grit your teeth and kneel. Maybe [W] was a bit too optimistic."
    "Viendo que no hay otra opción, aprietas los dientes y te arrodillas. Tal vez [W] fue un poco demasiado optimista."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4952
translate spanish d18f_cc37d9a2:

    # Q "Yes, this is how it should be."
    Q "Sí, así es como debe ser."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4953
translate spanish d18f_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4956
translate spanish d18f_0fdb5097:

    # Q "Do you think I should not have come to your house?"
    Q "¿Crees que no debería haber ido a tu casa?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4959
translate spanish d18f_6fc41b7e:

    # Z "You seriously thought...-"
    Z "En serio pensaste...-"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4962
translate spanish d18f_d6f3faca:

    # Q "Oh, wait! I don't actually care about your opinion, at all!"
    Q "¡Oh, espera! En realidad no me importa tu opinión, ¡para nada!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4965
translate spanish d18f_ea76183a:

    # "You're forced to remind yourself that she is the Queen, that she is impulsive and has, by all accounts, a mean streak."
    "Te ves obligado a recordarte a ti mismo que ella es la Reina, que es impulsiva y que, según todo lo que se sabe, tiene un lado cruel."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4966
translate spanish d18f_8649ef21:

    # "If you were to speak your mind, your survival is by no means guaranteed."
    "Si dijeras lo que piensas, tu supervivencia no estaría garantizada."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4969
translate spanish d18f_1f9ae7ef:

    # Q "Go to the training grounds. We will spar again."
    Q "Ve a los terrenos de entrenamiento. Volveremos a luchar."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4970
translate spanish d18f_23a84cc0:

    # Q "And yes, my blade has been sharpened..."
    Q "Y sí, mi espada ha sido afilada..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4973
translate spanish d18f_a10fa7b2:

    # Q "See you outside, Stalker. It will be fun..."
    Q "Nos veremos afuera, Acechador. Será divertido..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4981
translate spanish d18f_0731c493:

    # "The Queen is here!"
    "¡La Reina está aquí!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4985
translate spanish d18f_762597f9:

    # Q "Raise your weapon, Stalker! Your Queen commands you."
    Q "Levanta tu arma, ¡Acechador! Tu Reina te lo ordena."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4988
translate spanish d18f_0af044f5:

    # Q "...and this time, the fight will not end so quickly."
    Q "... y esta vez, la lucha no terminará tan rápidamente."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4991
translate spanish d18f_e15a5878:

    # "She looks gleefully at you. It is clear she means business."
    "Ella te mira alegremente. Está claro que va en serio."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4994
translate spanish d18f_1cca11b0:

    # "She approaches you..."
    "Se acerca a ti..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4997
translate spanish d18f_45ea66e0:

    # Z "No trickery, this time, hm?"
    Z "Nada de trucos, ¿esta vez, eh?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:4998
translate spanish d18f_89a19236:

    # Z "How noble of you..."
    Z "Qué noble de tu parte..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5002
translate spanish d18f_c57bb2d5:

    # Q "Shut up, [persistent.player_name], and draw your sword."
    Q "Cállate, [persistent.player_name], y saca tu espada."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5005
translate spanish d18f_eccb0c7f:

    # Z "As you wish."
    Z "Como desees."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5008
translate spanish d18f_a6c32bf9:

    # Q "Ha!"
    Q "¡Ja!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5013
translate spanish d18f_0f1944c8:

    # Q "...!"
    Q "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5014
translate spanish d18f_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5017
translate spanish d18f_2f4429cd:

    # Z "You think you can hide your emotions under a curtain of rage, don't you?"
    Z "¿Crees que puedes esconder tus emociones tras una cortina de rabia, verdad?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5020
translate spanish d18f_4eaccd4f:

    # Z "What's next? Will you force yourself into my house and imprison my family?"
    Z "¿Y ahora qué? ¿Entrarás por la fuerza en mi casa y encarcelarás a mi familia?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5023
translate spanish d18f_0d616f10:

    # Q "You should know... I have done much worse, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Debes saber... he hecho mucho peor, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5026
translate spanish d18f_b2f471fc:

    # Q "GUARDS!"
    Q "¡GUARDIAS!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5029
translate spanish d18f_c9707d98:

    # Q "Leave us! In fact, retire to your quarters."
    Q "¡ Dejadnos! De hecho, retírense a sus aposentos."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5032
translate spanish d18f_86a04767:

    # Fl "But... my Queen. What if you get wounde-"
    Fl "Pero... mi Reina. ¿Y si resulta herida?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5035
translate spanish d18f_937d7613:

    # Q "ARE YOU SAYING I WILL LOSE?! NO ONE WOUNDS ME! I am the Sacred Queen Merneith, have you forgotten?"
    Q "¡¿ME ESTÁS DICIENDO QUE VOY A PERDER?! ¡NADIE ME HIERRE! ¡Soy la Sagrada Reina Merneith, ¿lo has olvidado?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5036
translate spanish d18f_4892cf76:

    # Q "Now go away, [Fl] !! Before I change my mind and carve my name in your flesh!"
    Q "Ahora vete, ¡¡[Fl]!! ¡Antes de que cambie de opinión y grabe mi nombre en tu carne!"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5037
translate spanish d18f_1b598596:

    # Q "I do not want to be disturbed until tomorrow."
    Q "No quiero ser molestada hasta mañana."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5040
translate spanish d18f_c77e838b:

    # Flw "Do you think it is safe to leave her with... him?"
    Flw "¿Crees que es seguro dejarla con... él?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5043
translate spanish d18f_e6d33c67:

    # Gw "Queen's orders, brother. You have seen her in this mood before. Do you care to challenge her ruling?"
    Gw "Órdenes de la Reina, hermano. Ya la has visto en este estado antes. ¿Te atreves a desafiar su mandato?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5044
translate spanish d18f_0f684b4d:

    # Gw "We must trust her wisdom and obey her orders."
    Gw "Debemos confiar en su sabiduría y obedecer sus órdenes."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5047
translate spanish d18f_1451a4fa:

    # "They leave, muttering all the way out the door.."
    "Se van, murmurando mientras se alejan por la puerta..."

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5050
translate spanish d18f_d3908361:

    # Z "Are you sure that was wise?"
    Z "¿Estás segura de que eso fue sabio?"

# game/scripts/day18.rpy:5053
translate spanish d18f_ff30c581:

